		 * manager.addHandler( /\.tga$/i, new TGALoader() );
		 * ```
		 *
		 * @param {string} regex - A regular expression.
		 * @param {Loader} loader - A loader that should handle matched cases.
		 * @return {LoadingManager} A reference to this loading manager.
		 */
